INPUT:
    - m: Miner -       cost 100$ - 10$/s - sleep(1s)
    - s: Soldier -     cost 10$  - war()
    - x: 10 Soldiers - cost 100$ - war()

ZOMBIES:
    - Separate thread
    - Move: place--; if 0 attack();
    - Attack: 
        - if sol > zom: pos = 5, print_succ(fail...); 
        - else health-=zom-sol, print_fail(succ...);
        - zom *= 2 

GAMELOOP:
    - Gold change:    print_gold();
    - Soldier change: print_soldiers();
    - Health change:  print_health();
    - Zombie change:  print_zombies();
    - Health <= 0:    game_end();
